Titolo: Aztec: The Curse in the Heart of the City of Gold

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Aztec: The Curse in the Heart of the City of Gold (also known as Aztec: The Sacred Amulet) is a 2001 adventure game designed for Windows, PlayStation and iOS. It was developed by and published by Cryo Interactive (ported to the PS1 by Tek 5) and licensed by Wanadoo Edition.